channel.title: [639] Rune-Kingdom is back, 24 [NEW] Pictures!
channel.description:
[b]Rune-Kingdom is back, and [i]better[/i] than ever! When the project was first started, we reached over 1100 views and over 400 comments, but was soon removed due to leech acusations. It was later re-made, so no one can say this is a leech, it was created entirely by Rune-Kingdom staff. If ANYONE says this is a leech, they're paranoid, because I spent weeks developing this completley from scratch.[/b]
Before I release pictures, I would like to ask for ONLY beta-testers. I could use any and ALL beta-testers. All will get special permissions, such as mod and admin rights. I have a client for it, with a custom IP Set to direct the client to the server's host on socket 43594 (world 1) or 43595 (world 2). Reply or send me (Questmaster 2k10) a message. This server is going to be by [b]far[/b] the best one ever to be released to the public, as we already have major dungeoneering content.
Well, anyways here's the pictures I said I would add...Please note that this is all NEW Content, created by myself.
